long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension provides step-by-step AI-driven hints to help you solve LeetCode problems effectively. Designed for users tackling coding challenges, LeetCode Whisper seamlessly integrates into the LeetCode website to offer personalized, context-aware hints as you work through each problem. With an intuitive interface powered by Vite and React, this extension is perfect for developers looking to improve their problem-solving skills with guided assistance tailored to each problem's complexity and structure.
